item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: DanielDixon
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: DanielDixon
item.content:encoded: I am a Creative Digital Media student at the Institute of Technology Blanchardstown. I have a particular interest in Web Development and Web Design. Other areas in Digital Media I am experienced in include Graphic Design, Videography, Sound Design and Photography. This website showcases the best of my work.

item.title: Websites
item.dc:creator: DanielDixon
item.content:encoded:
Lucys Lounge Design

This is a website myself and three other students built as part of our second year group project. We built a website for a small vintage shop in Temple Bar which sells up-cycled clothing.Myself and the other students built the website from scratch taking all the photos and creating the videos on the site. Working with a live client was a great experience that thought me a lot. The site can be viewed at http://www.lucysloungedesign.com/index.html

Three Little Pigs Interactive Website

This was a project i created in second year. The brief was to create a parallax scrolling website while incorporating story telling. All the graphics for this project were also designed by me. The website can be viewed at http://threelittlepigs.dixonweb.ie/pigs.html

item.title: HOME
item.dc:creator: DanielDixon
item.content:encoded: I am a third year student currently completing a Bachelors of Honours in Creative Digital Media. I have a keen interest in web development and web design. Other areas i am interested in would be graphic design, film making and audio production. This website showcases the best of my work
